About the game: bullet rain Incessant attacks will leave you trapped not knowing what to do. Will his strategies be able to overcome the absolute combat power of his enemy's troops? Frantic Combat In this combat, keep in mind that the opponent will spare no efforts to eliminate you. Cyber Dungeon: Excalibur Cyber Dungeon: Excalibur is a rogue-like game in which you'll have to deal with a large amount of enemies and a suppression of bullets from all sides, in addition to having to be careful where you're going and where you are, so you don't end up getting lost in the levels and getting trapped in a dead end.
